room_title: Escape room "Voyager" by Portal Escape Rooms in Eugene
room_description:
13 billion miles away from earth drifts a spacecraft known as Voyager One. You and your crew awaken from an extended cryosleep with a serious case of amnesia and no contact with mission control. With little knowledge of what to do, you and your crew must rely on a number of artificial superintelligent robots for guidance.
Like all systems aboard the Voyager, these AIs are showing signs of deterioration. You must work together as a team to survive and track mysterious signals coming from the deepest reaches of interstellar space.
